{"tid":673840,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"比人類愛國！烏克蘭間諜海豚被俄抓走　絕食而亡","createTime":"2018-05-22T07:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T07:52:57.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1cc5cfcc05ae30bf9a234bb80ef5af5111814601","tid":673840,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:42:39.000Z","msg":"英國《衞報》報導，烏克蘭曾要求俄國歸還海豚，但俄羅斯希望用新技術，重新訓練海豚，但沒有成功。克里米亞烏克蘭政府代表巴賓（Boris Babin）近日稱讚海豚「為國捐軀」，指牠們拒絕聽俄軍指揮、絕食而死，表現出捍衞國家的情操，比一些士兵更值得尊敬。他說：「那些受過訓練的動物，不單拒絕與俄國軍官交流，而且絕食至死。不少烏克蘭士兵在宣誓忠於國家時，也沒有海豚這麼嚴肅認真。」<br />\n對此，俄羅斯國會議員拜利克（Dmitry Belik）反駁，為烏海軍服務的間諜海豚，大部分在2014年前，不是買給商業設施，就是自然死亡，根本不存在愛不愛國。<br />\n《衞報》指，過去有專家聲稱，海豚與狗一樣性格忠誠，會熱情地游向牠們見過的人，也曾有在飼養環境中生活的海豚，因為同伴死亡而絕食，所以烏克蘭的說法並非毫無根據。不過《衞報》承認，無法確認巴賓說法的真偽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180522/1358414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180522%2F1358414&d=v1TkUrlo%2B04KWALS5dTm4MVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=44bca994\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180522%2F1358414&h=71321ac7\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180522/1358414</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180522/640_a8768aabf03719772cbae3df31756a20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180522%2F640_a8768aabf03719772cbae3df31756a20.jpg&h=373a6eb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d22f26802865696360f021e2f4fc2eb6070c72","tid":673840,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:52:57.000Z","msg":"間諜海豚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}